# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ File name and class name are different.

✅ The file name must match the public class name.

---

❌ `main()` can be renamed.

✅ The JVM specifically looks for the `main()` method.

---

❌ `main()` must always use `args`.

✅ The parameter name can be changed, but the type must remain `String[]`.

Example

```java
public static void main(String[] names)
```

---

❌ Time Complexity measures execution time in seconds.

✅ Time Complexity measures the growth rate of an algorithm.

